{"id":161891,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/明報-解放軍月初海南島演習2036/","date":"2011-06-16T23:30:44Z","modified":"2011-06-17T05:47:21Z","title":"明報 | 解放軍月初海南島演習","content":"<p>解放軍報稱，海軍陸戰隊某旅6月初於海南海域進行跨晝夜搶灘登陸演練。</p>\n<div>\n<p>該部隊是利用野外駐訓時機，將部隊拉到海南陌生海域開展實戰化訓練，武裝泅渡、突擊搶灘等項目是演練重點。台灣中時電子報稱，消息在值南海主權爭議聲中，更顯弦外之音。</p>\n<p>解放軍報引述該旅旅長表示，這次登陸演練先後進行對空防護、長途奔襲、偵察防毒等20多個陸戰課目演練，探索出多種新的戰法訓法，進一步提升搶灘和構建登陸場等作戰能力。(綜合)</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&amp;ip=1&amp;img=1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&amp;ip=1&amp;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmingpao.feedsportal.com%2Fc%2F33528%2Ff%2F585672%2Fs%2F15ef3cd6%2Fl%2F0Linews0Bmingpao0N0Chtm0CINews0C20A110A6160Cca420A36c0Bhtm%2Fstory01.htm&amp;title=%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%9C%88%E5%88%9D%E6%B5%B7%E5%8D%97%E5%B3%B6%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92%5B20%3A36%5D\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\"> 定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a></p></form>\n","author":1,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}